{"tid":651994,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［沉船撚］一人一個死心方法","createTime":"2018-05-03T13:46:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T14:16:05.000Z","uid":63521,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"59a89b0f65d6dcf7839e4ed99868b06f55801a1f","tid":651994,"uid":63521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:46:40.000Z","msg":"鍾意左個有女朋友嘅男仔<br />\n好想死心 有咩方法<br />\n見住佢ig post哂條女 又紀念日咁<br />\n真係好唔開心<br />\n<br />\n本身個男仔想識我 搵我 <br />\n又話我係佢嘅動力 覺得我幾cute <br />\n本身諗住玩下就算 點知有日發現自己沉沉地船<br />\n但明知佢有女朋友都撩其他人 好極有限<br />\n佢應該唔止撩我一個女仔 應該仲有其他女<br />\n所以毅然決定唔覆佢 del 左佢sc 個啲<br />\n沉船還沉船 沉隻爛到咁嘅船會死人<br />\n都已經一兩個月了 我無搵你 你都無搵我 <br />\n但我好鍾意你 你知唔知<br />\n唔想做sp 或者 做第三者 <br />\n淨係想死心 有咩方法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e61664b19437692a4d12eb8adfa478e7ad2557","tid":651994,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:49:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">個人認為絲打可以一戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong><br />\n利申狗公 (發情期) <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5f6927d3dc959a8756c3af938ecea554fc3709","tid":651994,"uid":63521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"61e61664b19437692a4d12eb8adfa478e7ad2557","tid":651994,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:49:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">個人認為絲打可以一戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong><br />\n利申狗公 (發情期) <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"